    desc: "We help beauty salons, cosmetic clinics, and aesthetic professionals attract more bookings by improving their visibility on Google, building a premium and trustworthy online presence, and turning website visitors into appointment enquiries through conversion-focused website design, local SEO, and targeted Google Ads campaigns.",
    link: "/how-kiwi-web-design-helps-auckland-beauty-industry/",
  },
  {
    name: "How We Help Restaurants",
    img: "https://www.kiwiwebdesign.co.nz/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/restaurant-website-design-seo-auckland.jpg",
