  {
    icon: "📅",
    title: "Completed in 2–3 Weeks",
    desc: "Most projects are launched in as little as 2–3 weeks. This means you can start attracting customers quickly without waiting months for your site to go live.",
  },
  {
    icon: "📍",
    title: "Based in Grey Lynn, Auckland",
    desc: "We're proudly local, working out of 147 Great North Road in Grey Lynn. That makes it easy to meet face-to-face if you prefer, or we can connect online for convenience.",
