    icon: "🔧",
    title: "Focused on Tradies, eCommerce & Small Businesses",
    desc: "Our experience covers industries like trades, online stores, and local small businesses. From scaffolding companies to dental clinics, we build websites tailored to your sector.",
  },
  {
    icon: "⚡",
    title: "WordPress Specialists with SEO Basics Included",
