    sub: "Needs, goals, timelines",
    desc: "We hold a short discovery call to understand your service areas in Auckland, what success looks like, and what your customers need. This shapes the plan for web design in Auckland that suits your budget and timeline.",
    points: [
      "Goals, audience, and key offers for Auckland customers.",
      "Sitemap outline and content priorities that match local searches.",
      "Timeline and responsibilities so the project runs smoothly.",
    ],
    deliverables: ["One-page brief and sitemap", "Content outline and local keyword map"],
    duration: "30 to 45 minutes",
    cta: "Book a discovery call",
    ctaHref: "/website-designer-auckland/",
  },
  {
    num: "2",
    title: "Build on WordPress",
    sub: "Pages, SEO, performance",
    desc: "We build your site on WordPress using clean structure, fast hosting, and on-page SEO. The goal is simple: help Auckland businesses get found and get enquiries.",
