      "Page templates and reusable blocks for easy updates.",
      "SEO basics done: titles, meta, headings, internal links.",
      "Speed and mobile checks across common devices.",
    ],
    deliverables: ["Staging site and test plan", "Performance pass with core checks"],
    duration: "5 to 10 days",
    cta: "Request a build quote",
    ctaHref: "/website-designer-auckland/",
  },
  {
    num: "3",
    title: "Review & Launch",
    sub: "Testing, training, go live",
    desc: "We review content, polish details, then launch. You get handover, quick training, and a short report so your team is ready from day one.",
    points: [
      "Final checks, redirects, and basic analytics.",
      "Handover and short training for updates.",
      "Optional support plan for ongoing improvements in Auckland.",
    ],
    deliverables: ["Launch checklist and go-live window", "Simple performance snapshot"],
    duration: "Monthly",
    cta: "See support plans",
    ctaHref: "/#Services",
